query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) NoHashJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) NoHashJoin(acc b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('android',
'gaming',
'graphicdesign',
'travel')
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('adobe-photoshop',
'minecraft',
'visas')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Caucus',
'Citizen Patrol',
'Commentator',
'Custodian',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Question',
'Peer Pressure',
'Revival')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id;
